'''Nikola Radulovi<U+0107>''' (born 25 February 1993 in [[Pirot]], [[Serbia]]) is a [[Bulgaria]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as an [[attacking midfielder]] or [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[PFC Akademik Sofia|Akademik Sofia]] on loan from [[PFC CSKA Sofia|CSKA Sofia]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Footballdatabase.eu|title=Nikola Radulovi<U+0107> Facts|url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.nikola.radulovic.132037.en.html|accessdate=}}</ref>

